title: Death Rides the Megabus
description:
A traveller meets death on The Megabus.

Written by Katelyn Trela
Featuring Willy Appelman, Chrissy Shackelford, Tessa Hersh and Maya Deshmukh
Directed by Matt Gehring
Shot by Thursday Shoots
Edited by Phillip Russell
